Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Start of the Rainy Season
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Huh? What's wrong with Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}She just has a nosebleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're probably surprised\Nto see her covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, get me a bath towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing! Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SNIFF-SNIFF
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There's nothing embarrassing\Nabout a nosebleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, look at these big peaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How delightful! I love peaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There're so many. Weren't they expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did something happen to Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of, at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's okay. Everybody gets nosebleeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Do you often get nosebleeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}REALIZATION
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I never have.\N- You liar! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:19.78,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The type that does\Nas he's told
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Trying not to look
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some peaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe ice cream\Nwould've been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Peaches are good. I like peaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The cat's heavy! Can you move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.42,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LONG
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I'm gonna stay here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, we're going to the supermarket\Nfor the sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Keep lying down for another 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}STAMPS\NMAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}About Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Apparently her homeroom teacher\Ntalked to her after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Kawamoto, why aren't you\Ngetting along with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Why aren't I"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been like this.\NI told you then, about Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't raise your voice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, Ms. Kawamoto,\Nwhy can't you be more cooperative?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Suddenly, everything went red.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't just because of the sunset.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So until just a little while ago,\Nshe was furious and crying hysterically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She must have been frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mind went blank too when I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "How terrible."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hina...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll get called in for a talk soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one at our house who can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the other girl's parents\Nwill come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I hold my own against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do if they turn out to be\Nthose "monster parents" you hear about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}*Sending to you via imaginative video
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How dare your kid accuse\Nour cute daughter like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...should I unleash Monster Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done\Nto my granddaughter, damn it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if that doesn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there's the ultimate weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aunt Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we come to an amicable resolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}The Shadowy Monster\Nof Ginza *** Street
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One way or another!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? My alma mater\Nwill be engulfed in a sea of flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Aaaahhhhh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. Hina didn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there are so many people\NI can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Her hands...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}HERE TOO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:06:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He yelled!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dangerous! You're dangerous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey! Who are you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GASP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this! Quiet, Chibi and Meg!\NSorry to bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, Pochi! These people\Nare in the middle of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HERE TOO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:17.52,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PFFT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akari? Are you laughing at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.77,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WUFF\NWUFF
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.77,RightSignL3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BARK\NBARK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.77,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RAR\NRAR
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm ready for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}At last! At last, we made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more win for both of us\Nand we'll make it to the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}But a powerful enemy is lying in wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Last year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No, the Newcomer King\Namong Newcomer Kings! That man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEWCOMER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Because of that regulation for participants\Nbeing 5th dan or lower and under 26 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}that Junkei Yamazaki has been\Nthe Newcomer King for the last four years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*Sending to you via imaginative video
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this keeps up,\Nhe'll be the eternal Newcomer King!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:21.71,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal Newcomer King Celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that title\Nwould be an honor or dishonor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dishonor, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To all of us newcomers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right... for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't say "for once"!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You better not lose either,\Nto the Irritated Prince of the East!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Break him into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.65,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru Hachiya\N(5th dan)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been doing well lately,\Nwhich has made him even more irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Personality: The more he wins,\Nthe more irritated he becomes\N(three-stage reverse sliding scale)\NAttack: Fast Play/Tongue-Clicking\NFavorite Pieces: Bishop, Rook
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Attack: Fast Play/Tongue-Clicking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hachiya, huh? I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that tongue clicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Especially right now.\NI heard he's gunning for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you and I are the princes\Nof the next generation, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's worried\Nthat we'll steal his princely position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It even said so in Modern Shogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a variation on the Cheerful Rook\Nfrom the study group, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver to 3-2, Silver to 3-7, Pawn to 4-4,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and for Pawn 3-5, Pawn same,\Nand Silver to 4-6?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, a variation to the Bishop Exchange\Nwith the same pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how's Promoted Bishop to 2-8,\NPromoted Bishop to 4-4,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Promoted Bishop to 3-9?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But would Pawn to 2-2, Gold same,\NSilver to 3-3 be difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um, also, uh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikaidou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you think about Rook to 6-9?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nikaidou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That aside, you're going to Osaka tomorrow\Na day early, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's more important for you\Nright now to stay healthy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I opened the window,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}mixed in with the smell of the river,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was the scent of rain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}What is Hina doing right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Is she able to sleep all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be counting on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even when I do my best, I go nowhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't do what normal people can do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to help.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And yet, I don't know how I can be helpful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, I have no way of being helpful,\Nother than this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I want to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I want to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I want to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if it's just with one thing,\NI want to be strong for them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...want to be needed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Start of the Rainy Season
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hachiya
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If something happens, Ill be counting on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that time, when Akari's cheeks and voice\Nwere lit up by the setting sun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I can't get them out of my head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the first time, I feel desire for something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it isn't an innocent desire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether that's a good thing or a bad thing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Nevertheless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}...I want to win right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I want to win, no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Newcomer Tournament semi-finals...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I win this match, I'll go on to the finals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My opponent is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stomp around, Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Subaru Hachiya, 5th-Dan.\NTwenty-three years old, Class C-1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Out of all the professional shogi players\Nin their 20s, he's the most promising.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's trained at his workshop to become good\Nat playing fast and aggressively.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tongue-clicking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shaking his legs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tapping his folding fan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His nickname is the Irritated Prince of the East.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this world, strength is everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're strong,\Neverything will become justified.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's now 10:00. Please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it kind of bugs me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Cheerful Central Rook, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he intends to come at me hard and fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take this challenge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was fast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He really plays fast.\NMakes me wonder if it's on purpose.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:16:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TAP TAP\NTAP\NTAP TAP\NTAPTAPTAP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}And he's noisy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TAP\NTAPTAP\NTAP TAP TAP\NTAPTAP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I can't let it get to me though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It'll make it harder to focus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His defense is strong on the side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that means I just have to go from above.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's what he'll do,\Nthen I'll go Knight to 8-6.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Fast play, tongue-clicking, leg-shaking...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I put it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does he have to do all this to play shogi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can he think it's okay to behave like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can he sit there and not think about\Nhow his opponent will take it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An edge pawn?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Against the Edge King, push the Edge Pawn"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like that'll do the trick?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The freedom must be nice, behaving as you like\Nwithout sensing the other person's mood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's so slow it's getting me irritated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as I've got a dragon in this row,\NI'm going to be faster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Annoying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Man, he's annoying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}It's like I can hear the voices in his head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet he thinks the world revolves around him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-He's sacrificing his bishop?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}BISHOP{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't afford not to take it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:20:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I take it, I'll be one row off.\NThen the edge will be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He'll be able to swing the edge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did I make a mistake?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where was it? I didn't see that Bishop coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he going to checkmate me?\NNo. A faster move...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't there a fast move?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An even faster move?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If he'll get a bad temper when he loses,\Nhe should play more slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did a lousy job\Nremoving that "bee's nest!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You made him buzz even louder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be more cognizant\Nof the other players around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who suddenly starts poking the hive\Nwith a stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was on purpose, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There're a lot of other ways to deal with it,\Nlike wrap it in a bag and fumigate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BUZZ BUZZ BUZZ BUZZ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Hachiya-bee is always buzzing!\NHe has been since elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to change him now!\NSo we've all given up! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you can do is bag him\Nbefore he starts to buzz! Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you get older, it's harder to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So be more considerate!\NWe were playing an important match here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The next term's seed is on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you're older, it's tough\Nstarting a tournament from square one! Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to make it past this round!\NI lost though!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's so noisy buzzing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.51,0:21:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, youngsters these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi is too easy to understand,\Nbut Kiriyama, you're too hard to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should live so you're easier to understand.\NLike Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're both similar on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't compare me to him. I'm not—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think the world\Nrevolves around you, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SLAM
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we head out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there.\NThis is where Hachi really takes his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, the post-mortem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GRIND GRIND GRIND
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}RUMBLE RUMBLE RUMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make it a thorough one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KYAAAAA
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tongue-clicking. Leg-shaking. An attitude.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despite displaying all of these things,\Nhe's surprisingly loved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}TEAR TRACKS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Subaru Hachiya, 5th-Dan, 23 years old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TAPTAP\NTAP TAP TAP\NTAP
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Even after that, Hachi hung around Kiriyama{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and made him engage in a post-mortem\Nat a family restaurant until the wee hours of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the world revolved around him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't understand it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.08,0:22:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He yelled that a million times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}{\i1}GOBBLE GOBBLE\NTAP TAP TAP{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're not alike! We're nothing alike at all!{\i0}
